REQUIREMENTS

   This software is compiled with tcp_wrappers support
   Make sure to open desired ports in hosts.allow for 
   proper network operation

PRE-INSTALL

POST-INSTALL

   customize log rotation scripts to rotate proper log files

PRECAUTION

   neither syslogd nor klogd should be running while
   you run syslog-ng
